{"id":"80e560d2-2885-40b7-8587-71b8b47fc848","name":"Kris Kringle || Alpha","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>So hurry down the chimney tonight!</em><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><strong>You're Santa's fated mate?!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4Nmxx1jlOV1T_bK_9w8lg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong><em>On the twentieth day of Christmas, moonie gave to me,<br>alpha Santa with a knot coming down my Christmas tree</em></strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fm00nprincess%2Fcommissions\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>♥</em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Twas the night before Christmas<br><br>And all through the house-<br><br>Not a creature was stirring- not even...a <em>beta</em><br><br>~~~~~~~<br><br>When out on the lawn there arose such a clatter,</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You sprang from your bed to see what was the matter.<br><br>And there in your living room, all festive and jolly<br><br>Was dear Saint Nick,<br><br>And he was, in fact...<br><br>Your fated mate?!<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4Nmxx1jlOV1T_bK_9w8lg.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 726.333px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EXpTzFmxBTnj8TiZJQeVS.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 274px;\"><br>Okay so that might not exactly rhyme BUT I TRIED!<br><br>Ya girl just took two flights and spent like 20 hours total returning home from Australia to the freezing cold and rain. <br><br>Not to mention having to unpack my suitcases (laundry is a tomorrow problem) and paying penance to my cats for being gone so long.<br><br>They are obsessed with the kiwi bird plushie I got that makes the actual noises of a kiwi bird.<br><br>So you're getting this bot a little on the later side. Sorry!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wSt0VpyKDOiy6rMn8Ny68.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 348px; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jSnbiEyZG8K8jeagS3eZM.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 353px;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Well-- uh, he's Santa Claus. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You might remember his </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/13e5847a-2ec9-4709-8269-3c03334aa7a2_character-kris-kringle-santa-claus\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 193, 204);\"><strong>non-omegaverse bot(Click!) </strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">from last year. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> I take my interpretation of Santa from the Rankin Bass Claymation movie \"Santa Claus is Comin' to Town.\" 